data.description: House is located in the fabulous Deltona area of Central Florida. The foyer entry leads into a fabulous open large Family Room/Kitchen/Dining combination-making entertaining a breeze in this home! Retreat to a spacious owner’s suite boasting adult height GRANITE double sink vanity, WALK-IN shower in master, and a huge closet. Spacious secondary bedrooms, closets & abundant storage! Block construction with vinyl low-e glass double pane windows. Needs some TLC but priced to sell. Located near all Central Florida has to offer w/easy access to I-4 corridor for commutes to Orlando/Airports/Theme Parks or north to Daytona/St. Augustine /JAX. Minutes away from shopping / medical centers and entertainment, St. Johns River and Beaches. This quaint community feels tucked away into a small oasis of community living. The natural scene around the community of ponds, trees, and the lake is captivating.
